## Dataset Download

The PaySim dataset is not included in this repository because of its large size.

Download the dataset from:

Kaggle:
https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/ealaxi/paysim1

File used in this project:

PS_20174392719_1491204439457_log.csv

After downloading, rename the file:

paysim_transactions.csv

Place it inside:

Dataset/
└── paysim_transactions.csv

The dataset is then imported into PostgreSQL for analysis.
